data.description:
Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, two-story home nestled in the heart of Arlington. The exterior shows a charming facade situated on a prime cul-de-sac lot, offering both privacy and a sense of community. Zoned to the highly sought-after Martin High School, this residence is perfect for families looking to provide their children with an excellent education. Upon entering the home, you are greeted by a seamless blend of ceramic tiles and carpet flooring that adds warmth and style to the living spaces. The well-appointed kitchen boasts built-in cabinets, a convenient kitchen island, dual sinks, granite countertops, and a breakfast barperfect for culinary enthusiasts and entertaining guests. The adjacent living room features a beautiful fireplace, creating a cozy atmosphere for relaxation and gatherings. A convenient half bath on the main floor adds practicality to the layout. Venture upstairs to discover a spacious master bedroom, complete with its private bathroom retreat. The master bathroom offers a luxurious tub, dual sinks, a separate shower, and a walk-in closet, providing a tranquil space to unwind. Three additional bedrooms on the upper level accommodate family members or guests, offering versatility and comfort. Step outside to the large backyard, a perfect space for outdoor activities and entertaining. Whether you want to relax under the open sky or host gatherings with friends and family, this backyard provides the ideal setting. Keep cool during warm Texas summers with the pool, which requires maintenance at the tenant's expense, ensuring a pristine and enjoyable experience using WGC vendor services. This home combines practicality, comfort, and style, making it a fantastic choice for those seeking a welcoming and well-appointed residence in the heart of Arlington.

 Deposit, Pet Fees, Rents Due within 24 HOURS OF APPROVAL!
We do not advertise on FB Marketplace or Craigslist. 

All Westrom Group residents are enrolled in our RESIDENT BENEFIT PACKAGE (RBP) $45.95/MO - Includes renters insurance, HVAC air filter delivery (for applicable properties), credit building to help boost your credit score with timely rent payments, $1M Identity Protection, move-in concierge service making utility connection and home service setup a breeze during your move-in, our best-in-class resident rewards program, and much more!
